      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "周伯通笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖心想这总不是法子，但自己也不知该怎样出洞离岛，又问：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "周伯通道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "左手怎能和右手打架？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "周伯通停了手，笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说着伸出掌来。郭靖伸掌与他相抵。周伯通道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "speaker_name": "周伯通",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你懂了么？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "speaker_name": "周伯通",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不懂！",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "眼见郭靖脸有难色，央求道：",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖点点头，心想：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "周伯通又道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "speaker_name": "周伯通",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "兄弟，你身上倘若不痛了，我再摔你一交。",
