      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 694,
      "line_end": 694
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖一怔，料想必是喝了参仙老怪的大蟒药血之故，说道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 730,
      "line_end": 730
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "他喃喃的",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "四张机，鸳鸯织就欲双飞⋯⋯",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 736,
      "line_end": 736
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "周伯通叹道：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 738,
      "line_end": 738
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "speaker_name": "周伯通",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "郭靖见他神智胡涂，不知所云，心中大急，奔出洞去跃上树顶，高声叫道：",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 738,
      "line_end": 738
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_jing",
      "speaker_name": "郭靖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你⋯⋯你⋯⋯好啦！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 748,
      "line_end": 748
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "江南的医卜星相杂书",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 768,
      "line_end": 768
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说着哈哈大笑，高兴之极。郭靖问道：",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 780,
      "line_end": 780
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "周伯通只大笑不答，原来他忽然想到一个主意：",
