      "text": "笑道：",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 842,
      "line_end": 842
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说这话时，又已打好了主意：",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 846,
      "line_end": 846
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只记不用",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 852,
      "line_end": 852
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "见信上写",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "靖哥哥：西毒为他的侄儿向爹爹求婚，要娶我作他侄媳，爹爹已经答⋯⋯",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 878,
      "line_end": 878
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_bo_tong",
      "speaker_name": "周伯通",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他爹爹答不答允，不干咱们的事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 17,
      "line_start": 882,
      "line_end": 882
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "周伯通道：",
